{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"Restaurants and the food industry in general"},{"time":4000,"text":"are pretty much the most wasteful industry"},{"time":6000,"text":"in the world."},{"time":8000,"text":"For every calorie of food that we consume here in Britain today,"},{"time":11000,"text":"10 calories are taken to produce it."},{"time":13000,"text":"That's a lot."},{"time":15000,"text":"I want to take something rather humble"},{"time":17000,"text":"to discuss."},{"time":19000,"text":"I found this in the farmers' market today,"},{"time":21000,"text":"and if anybody wants to take it home and mash it later, you're very welcome to."},{"time":24000,"text":"The humble potato --"},{"time":26000,"text":"and I've spent a long time, 25 years, preparing these."},{"time":28000,"text":"And it pretty much goes through"},{"time":30000,"text":"eight different forms in its lifetime."},{"time":33000,"text":"First of all, it's planted, and that takes energy."},{"time":36000,"text":"It grows and is nurtured."},{"time":39000,"text":"It's then harvested."},{"time":41000,"text":"It's then distributed,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and distribution is a massive issue."},{"time":45000,"text":"It's then sold and bought,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and it's then delivered to me."},{"time":49000,"text":"I basically take it, prepare it,"},{"time":51000,"text":"and then people consume it -- hopefully they enjoy it."},{"time":54000,"text":"The last stage is basically waste,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and this is is pretty much where everybody disregards it."},{"time":59000,"text":"There are different types of waste."},{"time":61000,"text":"There's a waste of time; there's a waste of space; there's a waste of energy;"},{"time":64000,"text":"and there's a waste of waste."},{"time":66000,"text":"And every business I've been working on"},{"time":68000,"text":"over the past five years,"},{"time":70000,"text":"I'm trying to lower each one of these elements."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73000,"text":"Okay, so you ask what a sustainable restaurant looks like."},{"time":76000,"text":"Basically a restaurant just like any other."},{"time":78000,"text":"This is the restaurant, Acorn House."},{"time":80000,"text":"Front and back."},{"time":82000,"text":"So let me run you through a few ideas."},{"time":85000,"text":"Floor: sustainable, recyclable."},{"time":87000,"text":"Chairs: recycled and recyclable."},{"time":90000,"text":"Tables: Forestry Commission."},{"time":92000,"text":"This is Norwegian Forestry Commission wood."},{"time":94000,"text":"This bench, although it was uncomfortable for my mom --"},{"time":97000,"text":"she didn't like sitting on it,"},{"time":99000,"text":"so she went and bought these cushions for me from a local jumble sale --"},{"time":102000,"text":"reusing, a job that was pretty good."},{"time":104000,"text":"I hate waste, especially walls."},{"time":106000,"text":"If they're not working, put a shelf on it, which I did,"},{"time":109000,"text":"and that shows all the customers my products."},{"time":112000,"text":"The whole business is run on sustainable energy."},{"time":114000,"text":"This is powered by wind. All of the lights are daylight bulbs."},{"time":117000,"text":"Paint is all low-volume chemical,"},{"time":119000,"text":"which is very important when you're working in the room all the time."},{"time":121000,"text":"I was experimenting with these -- I don't know if you can see it --"},{"time":123000,"text":"but there's a work surface there."},{"time":125000,"text":"And that's a plastic polymer."},{"time":127000,"text":"And I was thinking, well I'm trying to think nature, nature, nature."},{"time":129000,"text":"But I thought, no, no, experiment with resins,"},{"time":131000,"text":"experiment with polymers."},{"time":133000,"text":"Will they outlive me? They probably might."},{"time":135000,"text":"Right, here's a reconditioned coffee machine."},{"time":137000,"text":"It actually looks better than a brand new one -- so looking good there."},{"time":140000,"text":"Now reusing is vital."},{"time":143000,"text":"And we filter our own water."},{"time":145000,"text":"We put them in bottles, refrigerate them,"},{"time":147000,"text":"and then we reuse that bottle again and again and again."},{"time":149000,"text":"Here's a great little example."},{"time":151000,"text":"If you can see this orange tree, it's actually growing in a car tire,"},{"time":153000,"text":"which has been turned inside out and sewn up."},{"time":155000,"text":"It's got my compost in it, which is growing an orange tree, which is great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"This is the kitchen, which is in the same room."},{"time":160000,"text":"I basically created a menu that allowed people"},{"time":162000,"text":"to choose the amount and volume of food"},{"time":164000,"text":"that they wanted to consume."},{"time":166000,"text":"Rather than me putting a dish down,"},{"time":168000,"text":"they were allowed to help themselves to as much or as little as they wanted."},{"time":171000,"text":"Okay, it's a small kitchen. It's about five square meters."},{"time":174000,"text":"It serves 220 people a day."},{"time":176000,"text":"We generate quite a lot of waste."},{"time":178000,"text":"This is the waste room."},{"time":180000,"text":"You can't get rid of waste."},{"time":182000,"text":"But this story's not about eliminating it, it's about minimizing it."},{"time":185000,"text":"In here, I have produce and boxes"},{"time":188000,"text":"that are unavoidable."},{"time":190000,"text":"I put my food waste into this dehydrating, desiccating macerator --"},{"time":193000,"text":"turns food into an inner material,"},{"time":196000,"text":"which I can store and then compost later."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198000,"text":"I compost it in this garden."},{"time":201000,"text":"All of the soil you can see there is basically my food,"},{"time":204000,"text":"which is generated by the restaurant,"},{"time":206000,"text":"and it's growing in these tubs, which I made out of storm-felled trees"},{"time":208000,"text":"and wine casks and all kinds of things."},{"time":211000,"text":"Three compost bins --"},{"time":213000,"text":"go through about 70 kilos of raw vegetable waste a week --"},{"time":215000,"text":"really good, makes fantastic compost."},{"time":217000,"text":"A couple of wormeries in there too."},{"time":219000,"text":"And actually one of the wormeries"},{"time":221000,"text":"was a big wormery. I had a lot of worms in it."},{"time":223000,"text":"And I tried taking the dried food waste,"},{"time":225000,"text":"putting it to the worms, going, \"There you go, dinner.\""},{"time":227000,"text":"It was like vegetable jerky,"},{"time":229000,"text":"and killed all of them."},{"time":231000,"text":"I don't know how many worms [were] in there,"},{"time":233000,"text":"but I've got some heavy karma coming, I tell you."},{"time":236000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":238000,"text":"What you're seeing here is a water filtration system."},{"time":241000,"text":"This takes the water out of the restaurant,"},{"time":243000,"text":"runs it through these stone beds -- this is going to be mint in there --"},{"time":246000,"text":"and I sort of water the garden with it."},{"time":248000,"text":"And I ultimately want to recycle that, put it back into the loos,"},{"time":250000,"text":"maybe wash hands with it, I don't know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"So, water is a very important aspect."},{"time":255000,"text":"I started meditating on that"},{"time":257000,"text":"and created a restaurant called Waterhouse."},{"time":260000,"text":"If I could get Waterhouse to be a no-carbon restaurant"},{"time":262000,"text":"that is consuming no gas to start with, that would be great."},{"time":265000,"text":"I managed to do it."},{"time":267000,"text":"This restaurant looks a little bit like Acorn House --"},{"time":269000,"text":"same chairs, same tables."},{"time":271000,"text":"They're all English and a little bit more sustainable."},{"time":274000,"text":"But this is an electrical restaurant."},{"time":276000,"text":"The whole thing is electric, the restaurant and the kitchen."},{"time":278000,"text":"And it's run on hydroelectricity,"},{"time":280000,"text":"so I've gone from air to water."},{"time":282000,"text":"Now it's important to understand"},{"time":285000,"text":"that this room"},{"time":287000,"text":"is cooled by water, heated by water,"},{"time":289000,"text":"filters its own water,"},{"time":291000,"text":"and it's powered by water."},{"time":293000,"text":"It literally is Waterhouse."},{"time":295000,"text":"The air handling system inside it --"},{"time":297000,"text":"I got rid of air-conditioning"},{"time":299000,"text":"because I thought there was too much consumption going on there."},{"time":301000,"text":"This is basically air-handling."},{"time":303000,"text":"I'm taking the temperature of the canal outside,"},{"time":305000,"text":"pumping it through the heat exchange mechanism,"},{"time":307000,"text":"it's turning through these amazing sails on the roof,"},{"time":309000,"text":"and that, in turn, is falling softly onto the people in the restaurant,"},{"time":312000,"text":"cooling them, or heating them, as the need may be."},{"time":315000,"text":"And this is an English willow air diffuser,"},{"time":317000,"text":"and that's softly moving"},{"time":319000,"text":"that air current through the room."},{"time":321000,"text":"Very advanced, no air-conditioning -- I love it."},{"time":324000,"text":"In the canal, which is just outside the restaurant,"},{"time":326000,"text":"there is hundreds of meters of coil piping."},{"time":328000,"text":"This takes the temperature of the canal"},{"time":330000,"text":"and turns it into this four-degrees of heat exchange."},{"time":333000,"text":"I have no idea how it works, but I paid a lot of money for it."},{"time":336000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":338000,"text":"And what's great is one of the chefs who works in that restaurant"},{"time":340000,"text":"lives on this boat -- it's off-grid; it generates all its own power."},{"time":343000,"text":"He's growing all his own fruit, and that's fantastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346000,"text":"There's no accident in names of these restaurants."},{"time":348000,"text":"Acorn House is the element of wood; Waterhouse is the element of water;"},{"time":351000,"text":"and I'm thinking, well, I'm going to be making"},{"time":354000,"text":"five restaurants based"},{"time":356000,"text":"on the five Chinese medicine acupuncture specialities."},{"time":360000,"text":"I've got water and wood. I'm just about to do fire."},{"time":363000,"text":"I've got metal and earth to come."},{"time":365000,"text":"So you've got to watch your space for that."},{"time":368000,"text":"Okay. So this is my next project."},{"time":370000,"text":"Five weeks old,"},{"time":372000,"text":"it's my baby, and it's hurting real bad."},{"time":375000,"text":"The People's Supermarket."},{"time":377000,"text":"So basically, the restaurants only really hit"},{"time":379000,"text":"people who believed in what I was doing anyway."},{"time":381000,"text":"What I needed to do was get food out"},{"time":383000,"text":"to a broader spectrum of people."},{"time":385000,"text":"So people -- i.e., perhaps, more working-class --"},{"time":388000,"text":"or perhaps people who actually believe in a cooperative."},{"time":390000,"text":"This is a social enterprise,"},{"time":392000,"text":"not-for-profit cooperative supermarket."},{"time":395000,"text":"It really is about the social disconnect"},{"time":397000,"text":"between food, communities"},{"time":399000,"text":"in urban settings"},{"time":401000,"text":"and their relationship to rural growers --"},{"time":403000,"text":"connecting communities in London to rural growers."},{"time":405000,"text":"Really important."},{"time":407000,"text":"So I'm committing to potatoes; I'm committing to milk;"},{"time":409000,"text":"I'm committing to leeks and broccoli -- all very important stuff."},{"time":412000,"text":"I've kept the tiles; I've kept the floors;"},{"time":414000,"text":"I've kept the trunking; I've got in some recycled fridges;"},{"time":416000,"text":"I've got some recycled tills; I've got some recycled trolleys."},{"time":419000,"text":"I mean, the whole thing is is super-sustainable."},{"time":421000,"text":"In fact, I'm trying and I'm going to make this"},{"time":423000,"text":"the most sustainable supermarket in the world."},{"time":426000,"text":"That's zero food waste."},{"time":428000,"text":"And no one's doing that just yet."},{"time":430000,"text":"In fact, Sainsbury's, if you're watching,"},{"time":432000,"text":"let's have a go. Try it on."},{"time":434000,"text":"I'm going to get there before you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436000,"text":"So nature doesn't create waste"},{"time":439000,"text":"doesn't create waste as such."},{"time":441000,"text":"Everything in nature is used up in a closed continuous cycle"},{"time":444000,"text":"with waste being the end of the beginning,"},{"time":447000,"text":"and that's been something that's been nurturing me for some time,"},{"time":450000,"text":"and it's an important statement to understand."},{"time":453000,"text":"If we don't stand up"},{"time":455000,"text":"and make a difference"},{"time":457000,"text":"and think about sustainable food,"},{"time":460000,"text":"think about the sustainable nature of it,"},{"time":462000,"text":"then we may fail."},{"time":464000,"text":"But, I wanted to get up and show you"},{"time":466000,"text":"that we can do it if we're more responsible."},{"time":468000,"text":"Environmentally conscious businesses are doable."},{"time":471000,"text":"They're here. You can see I've done three so far;"},{"time":474000,"text":"I've got a few more to go."},{"time":477000,"text":"The idea is embryonic."},{"time":479000,"text":"I think it's important."},{"time":481000,"text":"I think that if we reduce, reuse, refuse"},{"time":484000,"text":"and recycle -- right at the end there --"},{"time":486000,"text":"recycling is the last point I want to make;"},{"time":489000,"text":"but it's the four R's, rather than the three R's --"},{"time":492000,"text":"then I think we're going to be on our way."},{"time":494000,"text":"So these three are not perfect -- they're ideas."},{"time":497000,"text":"I think that there are many problems to come,"},{"time":500000,"text":"but with help, I'm sure I'm going to find solutions."},{"time":503000,"text":"And I hope you all take part."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505000,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]}]}